:INFO
Growing the Ginger Bug
In a clean jar, combine 2 teaspoons of grated fresh ginger (skin on), 2 teaspoons of \
white sugar, and 250ml of unchlorinated water. Stir well, cover loosely with cloth, and \
leave at room temperature. Feed every 24 hours with the same amounts of ginger

